Mike Schafier, an interests
log sophomore, has brought a
new sound to the Grinnell campus. No, he’s not the organizer
of a band, but of a hockey club.
The sound is of a shop shot responding off the boards of career Plaza Ice Arena.
The sign on the side of the
link cards: “No games of ally
kind", but Mike has Changed
that. He has made arrangements
